page.title: 06ECOLOGY--WOOD,FARM,WATER
page.content: {WOODLAND}(Deciduous & Coniferous) Beech,oak,ash,Norway spruce. Nettle- leaved bellflower,sanicle,woodruff, primrose,twayblade,bluebells,wood spurge. Tawny owl,sparrowhawk,green and great-spotted woodpecker,blackcap. Roe and fallow deer,fox,rabbits,stoats ,weasels,grey squirrels. Purple emperor butterflies.{AGRICULTURAL {LAND and HEDGES}Field maple,spindle, wayfaring tree,hedge garlic. Grey and french partridge,jackdaw,yellowhammer, skylark,lapwing,pheasant. Hare. {DOWNLAND and SCRUB}Rock rose,harebell, vipers bugloss,cowslip marjoram,thyme, campion. Woodcock, nightingale, blackcap. Green hairstreak, brown argus,small skipper,small copper butterflies.{LAKE and STREAM}Mallard, teal,tufted duck,pochard,Canada goose, coot,heron kingfisher,redshank,green sandpiper,snipe,water rail{continued}
